_:N3041eaecbba44e3bbabeb182443f0e49 <http://schema.org/description> "The Agri-Food and Biosciences Institute (AFBI) carries out research, development and testing for the Department of Agriculture and Rural Development, and other public bodies and commercial companies. AFBI (NI) is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department of Agriculture, Environment and Rural Affairs (Northern Ireland) ." .
